org.ldaptive
Class LdapResult

java.lang.Object
  org.ldaptive.AbstractLdapBean
      org.ldaptive.LdapResult
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class LdapResult
extends AbstractLdapBean

Simple bean representing an ldap result. Contains a map of entry DN to ldap entry.

mergeEntries

public static LdapResult mergeEntries(LdapResult result)
Merges the entries in the supplied result into a single entry. This method always returns a ldap result of size zero or one.

Parameters:
result - ldap result containing entries to merge
Returns:
ldap result containing a single merged entry
